title: Yunlaiju - Windlucky
description: Name in Chinese is 云来居素食馆. Address in Chinese is 深圳福田区香蜜湖度假村中国娱乐城大门南侧. Yunnan-style vegetarian dishes. Various types of mushrooms and herbs from Yunnan are used in the preparation of the dishes. Also serving a selection of pu'er tea. No eggs used. Directions: Located a the southern side of China Entertainment City, take metro to Honey Lake Station exit C, behind the Honey Lake automobile market.
streetAddress: Honey Lake Resort, Futain District, Guangdong
